"------------------------------------------------------------------------------
" Open, Save and Exit
"------------------------------------------------------------------------------
"| Commands     | Operation                                                   |
"|--------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
"| :e <path>    | Open a file to edit.                                        |
"| :w           | Save the current file.                                      |
"| :wa          | Save all of the files.                                      |
"| :q           | Quit.                                                       |
"| :q!          | Quit without saving.                                        |
"| :qa          | Quit all of the files.                                      |
"| :qa!         | Quit all of the files without saving.                       |
"| :x           | Save and quit.                                              |
